Package: wvschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process West Virginia School Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school enrollment data from the West Virginia
    Department of Education (WVDE). Provides functions for fetching Fall
    Membership (2nd month) enrollment data from WVDE School Finance Data PDFs
    and transforming it into tidy format for analysis. Supports data from
    2014-2025 covering all 55 West Virginia county school districts.
